  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: FortuneValley::FortuneValley.UI.Panels.RulesCarouselPanel
  _panelRoot: {fileID: 0}
  _slideTitle: {fileID: 1147643359}
  _slideBody: {fileID: 1280803393}
  _dots:
  - {fileID: 1744992699}
  - {fileID: 1938777857}
  - {fileID: 1771365978}
  _dotActive: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 29e905156af7a4474912c82650e04619, type: 3}
  _dotInactive: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6af6acd93ce1641ffa01a6eb09830b18, type: 3}
  _backButton: {fileID: 1852354332}
  _nextButton: {fileID: 805040032}
  _skipButton: {fileID: 913340073}
  _nextButtonText: {fileID: 350208258}
  _characterDisplayRig: {fileID: 563026380}
  _slides:
  - Title: Your Goal
    Body: "Buy all 5 city lots before your rival does.\n\nEach lot will cost more
      and more money, but the more expensive the store, the higher daily income bonus.
      \n\nThe one tool you have at your disposal that is unavailable to your rival
      is the stock market...\n\nBuild your strategy to beat your rival, whether that
      is investing heavily, lightly, choosing risky stocks, safe stocks, etc."
  - Title: How You Earn Money
    Body: 'Your restaurant earns $10 every day from the start, so you will always
      have a place to start.


      Lots you own also generate bonus income. The
      more lots you have, the faster your money grows and the more certain you can
      be in beating your rival.'
  - Title: Your Secret Weapon
    Body: 'You have an incredibly powerful potential additional source of income
      at your disposal, only if used right... the stock market.


      Be careful
      because too much risk can result in you losing everything, but play it too
      safe and you give your rival a better chance.


      Use the tools at your
      disposal to your advantage, build your strategy, but be careful, your rival
      won''t wait.


      Happy playing!'
